{"tid":1726851,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"第一步  點樣應對老解","createTime":"2019-11-16T09:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T09:44:29.000Z","uid":195158,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d768a7270b6997101aef4ce5f281edca92644efd","tid":1726851,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"如果奉行敵進 就我退，相信無人會接受<br />\n所以呢家唯有不變應萬變，再作觀察<br />\n<br />\n兩點可做<br />\n1）輸出革命<br />\n文宣要多做甴近平之路之類嘅文宣、<br />\n外加殘體文宣如8964，文革，貪污，唱衰中國新聞嘅文宣，密鋪地面，應有盡有<br />\n（總之，擊退5毛用咩內容就做咩文宣）<br />\n<br />\n2）遠離軍營<br />\n老解暫時會空裝上陣，全港有超過十個軍營，但唔係好集中，目的係保護重要基建。所以，以策安全同be water為由，老解營出面可照封，同鋪滿地文宣，但切忌硬碰，盡量保持距離。甚至重點堵塞遠離老解營嘅幹線，迫佢地行遠啲執石/上裝執石，已經對我地有利。"},{"pid":"50c33cd46cfd9582301513e46745d6267666212b","tid":1726851,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2992b297fcf7cff08b48768a68905dcaeb2f903","tid":1726851,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88137afe136ff2ceb82c8f0fdbe94b5c5c2dcd74","tid":1726851,"uid":222269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b31d14a033e80227fa4aa8b703932ac2e17e177","tid":1726851,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3660e4990d4720ac9eaf626483b1dd221acd9a83","tid":1726851,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"埋去挑機會點架?"},{"pid":"a466fdc41c7f33c6dde29ff2f427f72380186dc9","tid":1726851,"uid":195158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"753229fb312c40c667dac23dd25dce8538dcb4d9","tid":1726851,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3660e4990d4720ac9eaf626483b1dd221acd9a83","tid":1726851,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:34.000Z",