ttps://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=93a6b2aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=ddb2673f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"f7f6020777325902b07de51b82dd8c12dbbc7b10","tid":1726851,"uid":81500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37528a4497268f113c89af4ddf37d5f5429d7aa2","tid":1726851,"uid":195158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3660e4990d4720ac9eaf626483b1dd221acd9a83","tid":1726851,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"埋去挑機會點架?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"未上裝都唔好睇少佢地身手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇定啲唔使急，反正明顯對方更急<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢地一定有保護圈<br />\n<br />\n一堆防暴圍9住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:11.000Z","msg":"解防軍洗鬼防暴保護"},{"pid":"bcb6883b7475f8b8b3433c60e9eda9f6206186d7","tid":1726851,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老解同班狗有撚分別咩<br />\n都係會開槍殺人 你又唔係衝埋去死過<br />\n兩樣冇分別喎"},{"pid":"383f99013d24bc192ff0c93a5940f9d8156dda4d","tid":1726851,"uid":124372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:32:05.000